headline: 3 HMO Stocks to Watch Amid Nurse Shortages, High Tech Costs
summary: The Medical-HMO industry rides on steady premium flows resulting from a growing customer base and contract wins. However, industry headwinds like elevated technology costs and workforce shortages remain concerns. UNH, HUM and CNC are likely to navigate industry storms.

headline: Spotting Winners: Alignment Healthcare (NASDAQ:ALHC) And Health Insurance Providers Stocks In Q4
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Alignment Healthcare (NASDAQ:ALHC) and the rest of the health insurance providers stocks fared in Q4.
